channel.title: How can I add a thieving stall and edit how much XP it gives, money, ect
channel.description:
Hi I know this is really basic and I sound like a complete noob but can someone tell me where/how I can add a thieving stall? I also want to edit the money it gives you and how much XP it gives.
Thanks tons.

item.title: How can I add a thieving stall and edit how much XP it gives, money, ect
item.dc:creator: @Fatal_Desire Fatal Desire
item.description:
@Fatal_Desire wrote:

Client.Java. Search makeglobalobject. Put the Coords, then ID of the stall. Then search the ID of the stall in your client.java and if it comes up change the money amount. If not add it.

Read full topic
